            <title>[MAHOUT-161] Add Vector.norm to compute k-norms of vectors</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-161</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This patch adds Vector.norm(double power) to Vector (and an implementation to AbstractVector).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;AbstractVector.normalize now calls norm.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
